videos.description: Przemek Karnowski scored 10 points in the first 4 minutes of play for Gonzaga
videos.headline: Karnowski hot early for Gonzaga

videos.description: Joe Rahon makes the great layup through the foul to get the and-1 for Saint Mary's.
videos.headline: Saint Mary's Rahon makes great layup through foul

videos.description: Halftime interview with Gonzaga head coach Mark Few on the team's first-half performance without Nigel Williams-Goss, who was on the bench early with foul trouble.
videos.headline: Mark Few on Gonzaga's first-half performance

videos.description: The block by Jordan Hunter leads to a Calvin Hermanson Three Point Jumper for Saint Mary's.
videos.headline: Saint Mary's turns defense into offense to keep pace with Gonzaga

videos.description: Hard foul by Calvin Harrison sends Silas Melson to the floor.
videos.headline: Gonzaga and Saint Mary's getting physical down the stretch

videos.description: Nigel Williams-Goss talks about the teams focus and motivation after Gonzaga's 74-64 win over Saint Mary's.
videos.headline: Postgame interview with Nigel Williams-Goss
